    <briefdescription>
<para>DSSS spreading + root-raised-cosine pulse shaping (Phase B). </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Two pure DSP primitives the engine/composer use to build spread-spectrum and band-limited waveforms:<itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>wfm_dsss_spread: multiply each data symbol by a PN chip code.</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>wfm_rrc_taps: a unit-energy root-raised-cosine FIR (matched-filter pulse shape), applied by upsample + FIR. </para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
